rule.name: AS_QNM_UT_buildQuestions_TemplateFromReference
rule.description: Given a reference question, builds a template question by mapping the fields
rule.definition: #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_forEach"( items: ri!questions_Reference, expression: 'type!{urn:com:appian:types:AS:QNM}AS_QNM_T_Question'( questionReferenceId: fv!item.questionReferenceId, questionTypeCode: fv!item.questionTypeCode, label: fv!item.defaultLabel, instructions: fv!item.defaultInstructions, isDisplayedPrecedentSets: #"_a-0000e447-933d-8000-9baa-011c48011c48_66031"( questionPrecedentSets_Reference: fv!item.isDisplayedPrecedentSets ), isRequiredPrecedentSets: #"_a-0000e447-933d-8000-9baa-011c48011c48_66031"( questionPrecedentSets_Reference: fv!item.isRequiredPrecedentSets ), responseOptions: #"_a-0000e447-933d-8000-9baa-011c48011c48_40209"( responses_Reference: fv!item.defaultResponseOptions ), responseRequirements: #"_a-0000e460-9d93-8000-9bc1-011c48011c48_597588"( responseRequirements_Reference: fv!item.defaultResponseRequirements ), defaultResponses: #"_a-0000e447-933d-8000-9baa-011c48011c48_40209"( responses_Reference: fv!item.defaultDefaultResponses ), isActive: true ) )
